
The GHSL Dataset is too large. The raw form of it is 11,433 rows x 2,678 columns. Looking at the index, features have data every 5 years form 
1975 to 2015, then data every year from 2015 to 2025, then projections for 2030, 2040, and 2070

First we drop the future projects, as they lie outside the scope of our project. 



